'''探索龙'''（[[属名|属名]]：''Pitekunsaurus''）是[[阿根廷|阿根廷]][[内乌肯省|内乌肯省]][[白垩纪|晚白垩世]]{{link-en|阿纳塞尔托组|Anacleto Formation}}中的一[[属|属]][[泰坦巨龙类|泰坦巨龙类]][[蜥脚亚目|蜥脚亚目]]恐龙。 L. Filippi和A. Garrido在2008年对其进行叙述。[[模式种|模式种]]为马氏探索龙（''P. macayai''）。<ref name=FG08>{{cite journal |last=Filippi |first=L.S. |author2=Garrido, A.C.  |year=2008 |title=''Pitekunsaurus macayai'' gen. et sp. nov., new titanosaur (Saurischia, Sauropoda) from Upper Cretaceous Neuquén Basin, Argentina |journal=Ameghiniana |volume=45 |issue=3 |pages=575–590 }}</ref>属名取自[[马普切语|马普切语]]单词''pitekun''（意为“发现”），[[种名|种名]]纪念探险家路易斯·马卡亚（Luis Macaya），他于2004年4月发现了化石。

==分类学==
探索龙似乎是[[风神龙科|风神龙科]]的一属，与[[冈瓦纳巨龙|冈瓦纳巨龙]]和[[风神龙|风神龙]]的关系最为密切。<ref name=Cea13>{{cite journal | first1 = R. A. | last1 = Coria | first2 = L. S. | last2 = Filippi | first3 = L. M. | last3 = Chiappe | first4 = R. | last4 = García | first5 = A. B. | last5 = Arcucci | year = 2013 | title = ''Overosaurus paradasorum'' gen. et sp. nov., a new sauropod dinosaur (Titanosauria: Lithostrotia) from the Late Cretaceous of Neuquén, Patagonia, Argentina | journal = Zootaxa | volume = 3683 | issue = 4 | pages = 357–376 | doi = 10.11646/zootaxa.3683.4.2 | pmid = 25250458 }}</ref>它的{{link-en|脑壳|braincase}}与风神龙科的[[穆耶恩龙|穆耶恩龙]]以及[[地位未定|地位未定]]的泰坦巨龙类{{link-en|凡赫恩龙|Vahiny}}和[[耆那龙|耆那龙]]非常相似。<ref name=Wea09>{{cite journal | first1 = J. A. | last1 = Wilson | first2 = M. D. | last2 = D'Emic | first3 = K. A. | last3 = Curry Rogers | first4 = D. M. | last4 = Mohabey | first5 = S. | last5 = Sen | year = 2009 | title = Reassessment of the sauropod dinosaur ''Jainosaurus (="Antarctosaurus") septentrionalis'' from the Upper Cretaceous of India | journal = Contributions from the Museum of Paleontology, University of Michigan | volume = 32 | issue = 2 | pages = 17–40 }}</ref><ref name=CRW14>{{ cite journal | first1 = K. | last1 = Curry Rogers | first2 = J. A. | last2 = Wilson | year = 2014 | title = ''Vahiny depreti'', gen. et sp. nov., a new titanosaur (Dinosauria, Sauropoda) from the Upper Cretaceous Maevarano Formation, Madagascar | journal = Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology | issue = 3 | volume = 34 | pages = 606–617 | doi=10.1080/02724634.2013.822874}}</ref>在这一方面，不能将其与紧密相关的[[风神龙|风神龙]]和[[冈瓦纳巨龙|冈瓦纳巨龙]]进行比较，因为二者并未有颅骨材料发现。

